<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$peteryangsensei" href="/people/peteryangsensei">杨脑斯</a>，<strong title="北大临床心理学小硕。中学新人心理教师。" class="zu-question-my-bio">北大临床心理学小硕。中学新人心理教师。</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="6">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lk-lee" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lk-lee" class="zg-link" title="Lk lee">Lk lee</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ya-zi-61-48" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ya-zi-61-48" class="zg-link" title="牙子">牙子</a>、</span><span class="user-block">匿名用户</span>
